  EffectDiscription_ENG: "Burst Digivolve: 0 from [MirageGaogamon] by returning 1
    [Thomas H. Norstein] to handAt the end of the burst digivolution turn, trash
    this Digimon\u2019s top card[When Digivolving] Return 1 of your opponent's Digimon
    to the hand. Then, gain 1 memory for every 4 cards in your opponent's hand. [When
    Attacking] If your opponent has 9 or more cards in their hand, by choosing cards
    in your opponent's hand without looking and returning them to the bottom of the
    deck so that 8 remain, unsuspend this Digimon."
